  "instructions": [
    "mix sliced strawberries with coconut sugar, pickled ginger, and salt in a bowl.",
    "heat coconut milk in a saucepan over medium heat.",
    "whisk coconut milk until it thickens, then set aside.",
    "whisk together sesame oil, rice vinegar, and cornstarch in a small bowl.",
    "add sesame oil mixture to coconut milk and whisk until smooth.",
    "thread strawberries onto bamboo skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
